      <h1 >Central Library - 4th floor CLOSED</h1>
    
    
  
  <div class="content">
    <div class="field field-name-field-publish-date field-type-datestamp field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><span class="date-display-single">Monday, December 21, 2015 - 11:30am</span></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-all-full-text field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>Please be advised that the 4<sup>th</sup> floor of the Central Library is currently closed to the public for renovations. We apologize for any inconvenience.</p>
</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-affected-branch field-type-node-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Affected Branch(es):&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/branches/central-library">Central Library</a></div></div></div>  </div>
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
  
  
</div>  </div>
  <div>
    
<div id="node-109921" class="node node-alert contextual-links-region clearfix">

  <div class='breadcrumb'>
